Uses of Interface
demos.bags.Bag

  • Packages that use Bag 
    Package Description
    demos.bags  

    • Uses of Bag in demos.bags

      Classes in demos.bags that implement Bag 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  DynamicallyShuffledBag<Item>
      A DynamicallyShuffledBag is a Bag which, very much like a RandomAccessBag, shakes its contents completely (pseudo-) randomly.
      class  RandomAccessBag<Item>
      A RandomAccessBag is a Bag which, when RandomAccessBag.shake()d, essentially just shakes the index sequence into the old linear collection of Items.
      class  StaticallyPerturbedBag<Item>
      A StaticallyPerturbedBag is a bag where shaking perturbs the elements in a pre-defined way.
